{"tid":2099459,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"倍耐力願助國米簽美斯","createTime":"2020-07-08T08:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T12:43:56.000Z","uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d185e9a1bdec2d8cc1a65103d17ae4956e3d79d","tid":2099459,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"國際米蘭主要贊助商倍耐力透露，有意斥資協助球隊斟介阿根廷球王美斯。<br />\n<br />\n33歲的美斯（Lionel Messi）與巴塞隆拿洽談新約，陷入了膠著狀態，其合約將於下季屆滿，引起多支班霸虎視眈眈。 「坦白講，目前全球經濟不景氣，我們投資在體育方面的資金，難跟以前相比。」倍耐力行政總裁杜捷迪表示，願意全力協助國米斟介美斯，但強調藍黑軍團主席張康陽也要全力以赴，「我們可以出手，同時張生也要自己付出一點，我們不可能一手包辦所有資金。」 <br />\n<br />\n雖然巴塞否認美斯有機會離隊，但西班牙傳媒披露，阿根廷球王不滿球隊去年夏天未能重簽尼馬回巢，加上今季內部權鬥升溫，或使其他豪門有機會乘虛而入。"},{"pid":"d3976f7fd0bc41cc15b43f3bcdb1fedd1ccb8392","tid":2099459,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"美帝夥拍全能到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796cdcb2ef139e10249a5551be9549ac7ea112e6","tid":2099459,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:53:25.000Z","msg":"on9 球王緊係去返一樣級數嘅球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9a4b9fa579bbc7f4a6bfc4a78aff2c121d6019","tid":2099459,"uid":158755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"盧卡估打邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e93d15cb28055df09a92a49639f2a5ebabd024","tid":2099459,"uid":90515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"796cdcb2ef139e10249a5551be9549ac7ea112e6","tid":2099459,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:53:25.000Z","msg":"on9 球王緊係去返一樣級數嘅球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"去祖記痴冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1883de234f35fa11fb67d6c34dc0550b99c3fe0e","tid":2099459,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score